title: Warhammer Age of Sigmar The Realmgate Wars Set
description:
It's the perfect primer to get you up to date with the Age of Sigmar, and is packed full of epic battles, dangerous quests and loads of information about the Mortal Realms and the armies that fight to control them.

===================================================================================

Sigmar's might unleashed the Stormcast Eternals on the Chaos-ravaged Mortal Realms and changed the worlds forever. This collection of novels charts the great battles of the Celestial champions as they seek to open the Gates of Azyr, secure an alliance with the Everqueen and retrieve Sigmar's hammer, Ghal Maraz â€“ plus a tale of three Chaos Champions who want to join the ranks of Archaon's Varanguard.

This bundle contains the following books:

The Gates of Azyr by Chris Wraight
War Storm by Nick Kyme, Guy Haley and Josh Reynolds
Ghal Maraz by Guy Haley and Josh Reynolds
Hammers of Sigmar by Darius Hinks and C L Werner
Call of Archaon by David Annandale, David Guymer, Guy Haley and Rob Sanders
